Sway Keybindings Cheat Sheet
============================

Every Sway keybinding combination starts with the MOD key. In this configuration, the MOD key is set to the HOME button.

General
-------
- Open Terminal: MOD+Return
- Open Floating Terminal: MOD+Shift+Return
- Open Copilot: MOD+m
- Close Window: MOD+Shift+q
- Open program launcher: MOD+d
- Reload Sway: MOD+Shift+c
- Exit Wayland Session: MOD+Shift+e
- Show this Cheat Sheet: MOD+/

Window Focus
------------
- Focus Left: MOD+h
- Focus Down: MOD+j
- Focus Up: MOD+k
- Focus Right: MOD+l
- Focus (or open and focus) Firefox: MOD+w

Move Window
-----------
- Move Left: MOD+Shift+h
- Move Down: MOD+Shift+j
- Move Up: MOD+Shift+k
- Move Right: MOD+Shift+l

Workspaces
----------
- Switch to Workspace n: MOD+n (where n is 1-9)
- Move Container to Workspace n: MOD+Shift+n (where n is 1-9)
- Switch to the next workspace: MOD+.
- Switch to the previous workspace: MOD+,
- Switch to Empty Workspace: MOD+n
- Compact Workspaces: MOD+c

Screenshots
-----------
- Copy Area Screenshot to Clipboard: MOD+p
- Save Area Screenshot to ~/.screenshots: MOD+o
- Color Picker: MOD+Shift+p
- Toggle Screen Recording: MOD+Shift+r

Split Direction
---------------
- Horizontal Split: MOD+b
- Vertical Split: MOD+v
- Toggle Split Layout: MOD+e

Layouts
-------
- Fullscreen: MOD+f
- Toggle Floating: MOD+Shift+Space
- Toggle Focus Tiling/Floating: MOD+Space

Scratchpad
----------
- Move to Scratchpad: MOD+Shift+-
- Show Scratchpad: MOD+-

Volume and Brightness
---------------------
- Toggle Mute: XF86AudioMute
- Volume Up: XF86AudioRaiseVolume
- Volume Down: XF86AudioLowerVolume
- Toggle Mic Mute: XF86AudioMicMute
- Brightness Up: MOD+a
- Brightness Down: MOD+z

Misc
----
- Toggle Touchpad: MOD+t
- Dismiss Notification: Alt+Space
- Dismiss All Notifications: Alt+Shift+Space
- Emoji Picker: MOD+Shift+.

Resize Mode
-----------
- Enter Resize Mode: MOD+r
- Resize Left: resize mode + h
- Resize Down: resize mode + j
- Resize Up: resize mode + k
- Resize Right: resize mode + l
- Return to Default Mode: resize mode + Return
- Exit Resize Mode: resize mode + Escape
